text: Urban Dictionary is a website which is a dictionary of slang words. The website was created in 1999 by California Polytechnic State University freshman, Aaron Peckham. The website was listed as #29 in Time's list of 50 best websites of 2008. The website has been featured on Tosh.0's "words of the week". As of January 2011, Urban Dictionary has an alexa rating of 688. == References == == Other websites == * Urban Dictionary Category:1999 establishments in California Category:American websites Category:Online dictionaries
